title: New pool to add to Honey Farming
body:
Proposal to add new pools to TheHoneyPot Farming dApp.
- Shroom Farming will be closed after the poll has finished
- Arbys Rewards allocation will be reduced after the poll has finished
- All pools will be pool 2 with HONEY e.g Sushi LP tokens
